THE DEFENDANT WAS ARRAIGNED, CONVICTED AND SENTENCED TO ONE YEAR IMPRISONMENT ON COUNT ONE OF THE AMENDED CHARGE AND A FINE OF N100,000.00 (ONE HUNDRED THOUSAND NAIRA) AND ONE YEAR IMPRISONMENT ON COUNT TWO OF THE AMENDED CHARGE AND A FINE OF N100,000.00 (ONE HUNDRED THOUSAND NAIRA).
